name: DontHack.me
body:
Howdy Howdy! 

Welcome to the main landing page of the DontHack.me project! 
We are still working on a proper web site but for now this site has been put up. 
Our goal is to have a working sign up page by the end of July or early August. 

But if you want to get started now fell free to jump in! All of our work is being hosted on git in the project below: 
https://github.com/donthack-me

If you have any questions fell free to hit us up on Freenode, #Donthackme  

We can get you setup with a auth token and try to answer any questions as best we can :)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
